******* Please note before sending a bug report to the Debian BTS *******
*                                                                       *
* Please submit non packaging issue (e.g. feature requests) bugs to     *
* the Debian BTS _and_ the upstream BugZilla BTS (e.g. using bug-buddy, *
* http://bugzilla.gnome.org/buglist.cgi?product=bluefish) and put a     *
* reference to the BugZilla bug in the Debian bug report, to ease bug   *
* triage for the maintainers. Thank you.                                *
*************************************************************************

